```math
\frac{dy}{dx} = \tan{\theta}
```

両辺をxで微分

接線の傾き＝たわみの向き

```math
\frac{d^2y}{dx^2} = \frac{d}{dx}\tan{\theta}  
    = \frac{d\theta}{dx}\frac{d}{d\theta}\tan{\theta}  
    = \frac{d\theta}{dx}(1+\tan^2{\theta})...(g)
```

式(g)を変形して

```math
\frac{d\theta}{dx} = \frac{\frac{d^2y}{dx^2}}{1+\frac{\tan^2{\theta}}{\frac{d^2y}{dx^2}}} = \frac{\frac{d^2y}{dx^2}}{1+(\frac{d^2y}{dx^2})^2}...(h)
```

式(f)を(h)に代入
```math
\frac{1}{\ro} = \frac{1}{\sqrt{1+(\frac{dy}{dx})^2}}  
    = \frac{\frac{d^2y}{dx^2}}{[1+(\frac{d^2y}{dx^2})^2]^{\frac{1}{2}}}...(i)
```

$`\frac{dy}{dx}`$は非常に小さいので
```math
\frac{1}{\ro} = \frac{d^2y}{dx^2}...(j)
```

